---
// Korean variant of Ecosystem.astro. Tool names stay English (product names).
---

<section class="ecosystem section" aria-labelledby="ecosystem-title">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 id="ecosystem-title" class="ecosystem__title">SpecScore 기반 프로젝트.</h2>

    <ul class="ecosystem__grid">
      <li class="eco-card">
        <h3 class="eco-card__title">Rehearse</h3>
        <p class="eco-card__body">
          Markdown 네이티브 테스트 프레임워크. SpecScore 명세를 구현하는
          코드와 대조하여 테스트합니다.
        </p>
        <a class="eco-card__link" href="https://rehearse.synchestra.io" rel="noopener">
          rehearse.synchestra.io <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li class="eco-card">
        <h3 class="eco-card__title">SpecScore Studio</h3>
        <p class="eco-card__body">
          SpecScore를 위한 작성 환경 — IDE용 Claude Code 플러그인과
          심층 작업을 위한 웹 앱입니다.
        </p>
        <a class="eco-card__link" href="https://specscore.studio" rel="noopener">
          specscore.studio <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li class="eco-card">
        <h3 class="eco-card__title">Synchestra</h3>
        <p class="eco-card__body">
          SpecScore 명세를 중심으로 조율하는 AI 에이전트 오케스트레이션.
        </p>
        <a class="eco-card__link" href="https://synchestra.io" rel="noopener">
          synchestra.io <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ecosystem { background: var(--cream); }
  .ecosystem__title {
    font-size: var(--fs-h2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .ecosystem__grid {
    list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: var(--space-4);
  }
  .eco-card {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--graphite);
    padding-top: var(--space-2);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  }
  .eco-card__title { font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: var(--space-2); font-weight: 700; }
  .eco-card__body { color: var(--mid-ink); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.55; margin-bottom: var(--space-2); flex-grow: 1; }
  .eco-card__link { font-family: var(--font-code); font-size: 0.825rem; color: var(--ink-blue); border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor; align-self: flex-start; }
  .eco-card__link:hover { color: var(--ink); border-bottom-color: var(--ink); }

  @media (max-width: 800px) { .ecosystem__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-3); } }
</style>
